 220:src/voice.h   **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 1: round & dark power-chord bass (root + 5th + octave + sub) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌ
 221:src/voice.h   **** //   Same touch mappings, but osc2 is a fixed perfect fifth instead of a detune,
 222:src/voice.h   **** //   so every note sounds as a power chord. Lower range, gentler filter, less
 223:src/voice.h   **** //   drive ŌåÆ deep and round rather than bright and screaming.
